<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>والدِّهْلاثُ، والدِّلْهاثُ، والدَّلْهَثُ،<span class="c5"> والدُّلاهِثُ كُله:</span> السَّرِيع الجريء من النَّاس وَالْإِبِل.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَأَرْض دَهْثَمَةٌ ودَهْثَمٌ:</span> سهلة.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَرجل دَهْثَمُ الْخلق:</span> سهله.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">ودَهْثَمٌ:</span> اسْم.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وثَهْمَدٌ:</span> مَوضِع.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">والرَّهْدَلُ:</span> طَائِر شبه الْحمرَة،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ ثَعْلَب:</span> هُوَ طَائِر شبه القبرة إِلَّا إِنَّهَا لَيست لَهَا قنزعة.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">والرَّهْدَلُ:</span> الأحمق،<span class="c5"> وَقيل:</span> الضَّعِيف.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>والرَّهْدَنُ، والرَّهْدَنَة والرُّهْدُونُ، كالرهدل الَّذِي هُوَ الطَّائِر الْمُتَقَدّم ذكره.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">والرَّهْدَن:</span> الأحمق، كالرهدل،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>قُلتُ لَهَا إيَّاكِ أنْ تَوَكَّنِي<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>عِنْدِي فِي الجَلْسَةِ أوْ تَلَبَّنِي<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>علَيْكِ مَا عِشْتِ بذَاكَ الرَّهدَنِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">والرُّهْدُونُ:</span> الْكذَّاب.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">والرَّهدَنَة:</span> الإبطاء، وَقد رَهْدَنَ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>فجِئْتُ بالنَّقدِ وَلم أُرَهْدِنِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>أَي لم أبطئ وَلم احْتبسَ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">والدُّهْدُنُّ:</span> الْبَاطِل،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>لأَجْعَلَنْ لاِبْنَةِ عَمْرٍو فَنَّا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>حَتَّى يَكُونَ مَهْرُها دُهْدُنَّا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c5">ويروى:</span> <span class="c1">" لابنَة غنم "</span>.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>